descriptionHTML:
Synchronization can take several MINUTES, please be patient you have 2 hours for refund.

This Android Wear watch face introduces a new concept of animated background that allow to invent any scenario.
The background is animated like a true watchmaker mechanical watch revealing the sophistication of its mechanism.
Switzerland wish to share with you its love for precise mechanic and hope you will enjoy it.
If you wish to realise yours we are available on our web site AiM Services (www.aim-services.ch).
The animation is based on a 3D model built with the TellWatch software.
comments: Suspicious app Does not ever show up in the faces selection and slows the watch WAY down.
